<title>USA: Motorola inks pact with Security Dynamics.</title>
<headline>Motorola inks pact with Security Dynamics.</headline>
<dateline>SCHAUMBURG, Ill. 1997-01-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Motorola Inc said Tuesday it signed a licensing agreement under which a unit of Security Dynamics Technologies Inc will provide security technology to Motorola.</p>
<p>Motorola said the technology from RSA Data Security will be used in various applications throughout all of Motorola's business segments. RSA provides encryption and authentification technologies to software developers.</p>
<p>Motorola is a global communications products and services provider.</p>
<p>Its shares closed up 2-1/8 Tuesday at 66-7/8.</p>
<p>((Chicago newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
